---
title: Cheese Tortellini in Tomato-Bacon Sauce with Spinach and Parmesan
description: Bacon really does go with everything, especially mushrooms and tomatoes! Cheesy tortellini are the perfect pasta to sop up all the delicious sauce.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cheese-tortellini-in-tomato-bacon-sauce-faafaa02.jpg
